Install:
    git clone git://github.com/maxwellc/makedoc.git

Usuage:
    Populates a file with the docstrings from
    a module you specify, using pydocs. Use from the
    command line within your script's directory.
    eg python makedoc.py fileToWriteTo moduleName

Sample Output:
*******************
Python Library Documentation: module nameOfModule

NAME
    nameOfModule

FILE
    /path/to/module/modulename.py

FUNCTIONS
    bar()
    Use this function to do something else...
                        
    foo()
    Use this function to....
*******************
